    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Oakley and Elmer on their whimsical adventure through a stunning archipelago filled with people to befriend and secrets to uncover. Though simply tasked with finding a strange mythical creature, the two robots are distracted by the beauty of the islands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore and Discover</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, climb, and crawl across the islands as you collect and find new items and tools! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Be a part of the Community!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Why are we always so pressured by efficiency? Work together with many fun and quirky people as you each learn to relax and enjoy the beauty around you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unwind in a Recovering Paradise</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Although on a top secret mission, the distractions here are plentiful! <i>Surely our bosses won’t mind if we fish for a little while longer.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042040/extras/430d8031f9363a499140ec4463f2c22c.poster.avif?t=1759101181\" width=308 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042040/extras/430d8031f9363a499140ec4463f2c22c.webm?t=1759101181\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
